&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="question3-kubernetes-cluster-configuration-includes-providing-a-cidr-range-for-kubernetes-services-and-a-cidr-range-for-pods--select-all-that-apply----omit-in-toc---">&lt;strong>Question3:&lt;/strong> Kubernetes cluster configuration includes providing a CIDR range for Kubernetes services and a CIDR range for pods. || Select all that apply.: &lt;!-- omit in toc -->&lt;/h4>
